Deathwatch		KEY:Deathwatch ~ Unchosen	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Sense		DESC:The tampering with the unchosen's brain has granted the creature the ability to "scent life." As long as targets are in range of the unchosen's scent ability, it instantly knows whether each creature in the area is dead, fragile (alive and wounded with 3 or fewer hit points left), fighting off death (alive with 4 or more hit points), undead, or neither alive nor dead (such as a construct).														SOURCEPAGE:p.88
Ferocity		KEY:Ferocity ~ Unchosen		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary.Defensive	DESC:An unchosen remains conscious and continues fighting even if its hit point total is below 0. The unchosen is still staggered and loses 1 hit point each round, but it gains a +2 bonus on attack rolls and all weapon damage rolls. The unchosen still dies when its hit point total reaches -%1.|CONSCORE																														SOURCEPAGE:p.88
Foresighted		KEY:Foresighted ~ Unchosen	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Defensive	DESC:An unchosen's trepanation has partially unlocked an almost psychic ability to sense peril. It gains a +2 insight bonus on Initiative checks and to its armor class.																																							BONUS:COMBAT|AC|2|TYPE=Insight	BONUS:COMBAT|Initiative|2|TYPE=Insight	SOURCEPAGE:p.88

